{"title":"看看谁坐村“朝廷”","authors":["叶枫"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看谁坐村“朝廷”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶枫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我进城里去送信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路过二区泗沟村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听锣鼓喧天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我思想：这又是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家翻身唱戏文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不然，一定是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥儿们光景好过了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹吹打打娶新人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进了大街往前行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓声响步步近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头一看吃一惊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位穿件破衫人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圪茬胡子长半寸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸皮茄子一样青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上披条红绳绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是个犯罪人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他，慢吞吞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步，打下锣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走两步，唉一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似没有吃饱饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似苦事痛在心。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打鼓的紧相跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚咙咙可吃劲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象位当差接官令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直着脖子喊连声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他小名，叫丑丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争果实想多分。………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街两旁站满人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个议论纷纷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我奇怪，闹不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双脚不觉站不稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻在里边听一听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山羊胡伯伯说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“丑丁是个最穷的穷人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没房没地赤背身。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红眼睛哥儿讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“分给丑丁三间房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房顶窟窿露星星。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛着枪杆小民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍拍胸膛说得清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要是我当跑腿的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不擂鼓也不吭声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起来，真亏心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下穷汉一家人！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃脑瓜叔叔说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这事情，我摸的清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评议员评了八天整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家可也费了心！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，决定这意见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明日，重改又换新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说：斗争积极要多分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说：干部辛苦应多分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说：中贫赤农一样分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七嘴八舌乱哼哼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再开八天也闹不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长一听气愤愤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴巴张开下命令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这事不用多讨论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分给谁啥就要啥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要吭声叫反省！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反省不好叫游行！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看制了咱丑丁。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白头爷爷发了急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气气呼呼吼连声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“村长耳朵不管用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不听咱赤贫的反映，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长没有长眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不看咱赤贫是啥光景。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，有一位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿身细布中年人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇摇脑袋说分明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“各人心中要自问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长给咱办事情。……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等他，往下讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家轰轰说一阵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“村长给你办事情！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你是中农心高兴！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“斗争果实分不分！？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱们受饥挨雨淋！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住圪节我说啦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“赤贫户比咱受苦大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果实要先尽他们分。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家齐说：“这公平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：“中贫赤农是一家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑马坐轿没有咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都要翻透身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身来过好光景。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家听了都高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忙撤腿去送信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走出了泗沟村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中转着这事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决定进城送个信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲给县上领导听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看谁坐村“朝廷”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“圪节”即问题关键豫北人民土话。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}